{"title":"This Custom Titanium Firefly Mini Velo Fits in a Rimowa Case","link":"https://theradavist.com/firefly-mini-velo-rimowa-case/","date":1708536604000,"content":"<p><img width=\"4862\" height=\"3242\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Firefly_mini-velo-Rimowa-Case.jpg?fit=1200,3242&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Firefly_mini-velo-Rimowa-Case.jpg?w=4862&amp;quality=75 4862w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Firefly_mini-velo-Rimowa-Case.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Firefly_mini-velo-Rimowa-Case.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Firefly_mini-velo-Rimowa-Case.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Firefly_mini-velo-Rimowa-Case.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Firefly_mini-velo-Rimowa-Case.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>If we won the lottery, there would be signs! A customer commissioned <a href=\"https://fireflybicycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Firefly</a> to make a coupled titanium mini bike to fit inside a <a href=\"https://www.rimowa.com/my/en/luggage/colour/black/check-in-l/92573014.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rimowa case</a> for easy travel with a bike. This sort of bike is peak custom, so we had to get a closer look…<span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-1_53510049352_o.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-1_53510049352_o.jpg?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-1_53510049352_o.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-1_53510049352_o.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-1_53510049352_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-1_53510049352_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-1_53510049352_o.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The idea was to make a lightweight and durable chassis, that broke into halves and packed away into the constraints of the Rimowa case for ease of checked luggage.</p>\n<p><img width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-26_53511260139_o.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-26_53511260139_o.jpg?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-26_53511260139_o.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-26_53511260139_o.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-26_53511260139_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-26_53511260139_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-26_53511260139_o.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-29_53511106773_o.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-29_53511106773_o.jpg?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-29_53511106773_o.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-29_53511106773_o.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-29_53511106773_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-29_53511106773_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-29_53511106773_o.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Using hydraulic line couples inside the frame, Firefly created a smooth user experience.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"5184\" height=\"3456\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-8_53511260354_o.jpg?fit=1200,3456&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-8_53511260354_o.jpg?w=5184&amp;quality=75 5184w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-8_53511260354_o.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-8_53511260354_o.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-8_53511260354_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-8_53511260354_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-8_53511260354_o.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-11_53510940166_o.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-11_53510940166_o.jpg?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-11_53510940166_o.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-11_53510940166_o.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-11_53510940166_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-11_53510940166_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-11_53510940166_o.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>This project was made possible by Firefly’s custom, 3D printed forks.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-17_53511107043_o.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-17_53511107043_o.jpg?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-17_53511107043_o.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-17_53511107043_o.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-17_53511107043_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-17_53511107043_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-17_53511107043_o.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-6_53510049092_o.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-6_53510049092_o.jpg?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-6_53510049092_o.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-6_53510049092_o.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-6_53510049092_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-6_53510049092_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-6_53510049092_o.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The wheels are ultralight SMC Govan tri-spokes. As with every custom Firefly, the titanium frame becomes a canvas for custom anodizing…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-4_53511107143_o.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-4_53511107143_o.jpg?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-4_53511107143_o.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-4_53511107143_o.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-4_53511107143_o.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-4_53511107143_o.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/ff-1323-studio-4_53511107143_o.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>When it comes to luxury, some people spend thousands on designer shoes and purses, and others, custom bicycles.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Mini-Velo-Geometry.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Mini-Velo-Geometry.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Mini-Velo-Geometry.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Mini-Velo-Geometry.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Mini-Velo-Geometry.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Full geometry…</p>\n<p><strong>Build Spec:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Rear Derailleur: SRAM Red AXS</li>\n<li>Battery and charder: SRAM AXS</li>\n<li>Cranks: eeWings Allroad, 170mm, blasted to match frame</li>\n<li>Chainring: Alugear Round for SRAM 3-bolt, red, 56t</li>\n<li>Shifters: SRAM Red AXS</li>\n<li>Brake levers: Sturdy Ti</li>\n<li>Brakes: Hope RX4+, flat-mount, red</li>\n<li>Brake line couplers: Zeno Q Connector x2, with Fix Pin and Pin Keeper Ring</li>\n<li>Disc rotors: Carbon-Ti X-Rotor SteelCarbon 3, 160mm front and 160mm rear, 6-bolt with centerlock adapters</li>\n<li>Rotor adapters: 6-bolt to centerlock</li>\n<li>Cassette: SRAM Red AXS, 10-33</li>\n<li>Chain: SRAM Red AXS</li>\n<li>Bottom Bracket: Chris King T47 30x, ceramic, red</li>\n<li>Headset: Firefly Ti</li>\n<li>Bar/stem: Blacksheep</li>\n<li>Tires: Michelin Pilot SX Slick, 20×1.7″, black</li>\n<li>Tubes: Tubolito Tubo x4</li>\n<li>Valve extenders: Problem Solvers</li>\n<li>Wheels: SMC Govan 406-TW3 20″ 406, ceramic hubs, 12k matte finish, CL</li>\n<li>Axles: RapiLock Axle 105</li>\n<li>Seatpost: Firefly Ti, includes Ti seat collar</li>\n<li>Saddle: Specialized Power Pro with Mirror, 155mm</li>\n<li>Bartape: BTP Woven Chima Red</li>\n<li>Bottle cages: Silca Ti x1</li>\n<li>Pedals: Crankbrothers Eggbeater 3, red</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Thanks to <a href=\"https://fireflybicycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Firefly</a> for sending this over!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/firefly-mini-velo-rimowa-case/\">This Custom Titanium Firefly Mini Velo Fits in a Rimowa Case</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"93ed6ec3ddc567957c7030e281e6c1dca5f218c4a0e6a408701dcb5d85c86a2a","category":"Cycling"}